Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The property features a 11,900 sq. ft. truck shop on 17.52 acres, with additional 3,200 sq. ft. sandblasting shop on site. Gravel / compacted yard and drive-thru loading. Main shop can be demised for two tenants. Truck shop features a fire suppression system.

Unique industrial shop complex on 6.65 acres. Includes oversized grade loading doors, 80' clear span, and in floor heating. Full municipal services. Shop features one 3-ton and three 5-ton cranes, full fire suppression system, and full municipal services.

9,288 sq. ft. two storey office building with an additional 1,500 sq. ft. modular office structure on a 2.04 acre hard surfaced site. Built between 2011 and 2015, the property includes full municipal services.
